Analyze how competitors in the AI content tools space ({competitor_info}) approach social media content. Identify {count} content gaps or angles they miss that GoUltra AI can own.

Our positioning: {brand_info}
Topic area: {topic}

Respond ONLY as a JSON array with: title, angle, hook, type, platforms, cta_suggestion, reasoning, suggested_tags.

Expand the content pillar '{pillar}' into {count} diverse post ideas for GoUltra AI.

Vary types (image, carousel, video, text), angles (educational, provocative, storytelling, data-driven), and depth.

Platforms: {platforms}
Audience: {audience}

Respond ONLY as a JSON array.

Create a {count}-post story arc that takes the audience on a journey:

Story: {story_brief}
Arc: Problem → Exploration → Solution → Proof → Action

Each post should feel complete on its own but contribute to the larger narrative.

Platforms: {platforms}
Audience: {audience}

Respond ONLY as a JSON array with: title, arc_position (1-N), angle, hook, type, platforms, cta_suggestion, reasoning.
